The Wife of Bauchi State Governor, Hajiya Aisha Bala Mohammed, has donated empowerment tools to vulnerable women in the spirit of the holy month of Ramadan across the 20 Local Government Areas of the state Mrs Bala said the empowerment was aimed at easing the hardship that most women in the local government areas experience, adding that the gesture would be extended every month of Ramadan. She cautioned the women leaders from the 20 LGAs to ensure that they extended the items to the needy in their areas.